The paper presents a novel approach for classification using feature-space decomposition, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of parallel processing for large-scale data sets, which is relevant to distributed systems (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper mentions experiments on image data sets (cs.CV) and proposes a new classifier (cs.NE).
